1) download source from http://www.stlsoft.org/
2) unzip to library/stlsoft - should look like

dev/library/stlsoft % ll
AUTHORS.txt
CHANGES.txt
FAQ.txt
HISTORY.txt
HOW_YOU_CAN_HELP.txt
include/
INSTALL.txt
KNOWN_ISSUES.txt
LICENSE.txt
NEWS.txt
README.txt
TODO.txt
dev/library/stlsoft %

3) move all include libaries to current directory

mv include/* . && rmdir include

Now looks like this:

dev/library/stlsoft % ls -1
acestl/
atlstl/
AUTHORS.txt
CHANGES.txt
comstl/
dotnetstl/
FAQ.txt
HISTORY.txt
HOW_YOU_CAN_HELP.txt
inetstl/
INSTALL.txt
KNOWN_ISSUES.txt
LICENSE.txt
mfcstl/
NEWS.txt
platformstl/
rangelib/
README.txt
stlsoft/
TODO.txt
unittest/
unixstl/
winstl/
wtlstl/
dev/library/stlsoft %

